'''''Tower of Myraglen''''' is an [[adventure game|adventure]] [[role-playing video game]] published by PBI Software.  It was released for the [[Apple IIGS]] in 1987.

==Plot==
The [[player character]] is a Knight of Justice sent by the King of Myraglen to retrieve the Medallion of Soul Stealing from the Tower of Myraglen.<ref name="Dragon129"/>

==Reception==
The game was reviewed in 1988 in ''[[Dragon (magazine)|Dragon]]'' #129 by Hartley, Patricia, and Kirk Lesser in "The Role of Computers" column. The reviewers gave the game 3½ stars.<ref name="Dragon129">{{cite journal
